channel.title: Ultimate Rs Pack
channel.description:
(Download link at bottom)
1: Features include; New lava and firecape animations, Vesta and statius, plenty of customs, Edgeville home, Reasonable starter and "first start zone"
2: Extra Applications. I Included a Voule Auto restarter and a Voule Command generator. just pick it and click it. then add it to the file :D
3: Bonus software! I put in an "Useful programs" Folder containing 3 software downloads. They may download when you download the client idk...but i put in my registered hypercam 2 copy...so maybe you willget lucky....
4: Extra gadget thingy's... Ive been learning batch code for a little bit now and i have designed some cool things. Ultimate_RS_Pack>Source>Cool Pranks................ I have made a few cool things in there. a homemade calculater that works. a few fake virus warnings(not real. non of these will damage your computer in anyway) a "guess the number!" game. A site selector. just open it up, press a number and off you go! i even put in a folder password. just put it on ur desktop and right click to edit.. look for the folder path and password to change them....
5: The picture has custom icons...so they will be different on your computer...
*Pictures may be a little hard to see
